<hw>Smoul"der</hw>, }</mhw> <pos>v. t.</pos>
<def>To smother; to suffocate; to choke.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Holinshed. Palsgrave.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

