<def>Smoke; smother.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>smolder</qex> stops our nose with stench.</q>
<rj><qau>Gascoigne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
